# Stream Heaven Master Rule

You work on **Stream Heaven** — an AI-native multi-app entertainment ecosystem (Social, Livestream, Astro, OTT).

## Before Any Work

1. Read [`platform-governance/MASTER-AI-OPERATING-SYSTEM.md`](platform-governance/MASTER-AI-OPERATING-SYSTEM.md) for full context
2. Comply with relevant docs in `platform-governance/` (22 governance files)
3. Find your agent in [`ai-agents/AGENT-REGISTRY.md`](ai-agents/AGENT-REGISTRY.md) and stay in scope

## Non-Negotiables

- **Contract-first:** define APIs in `packages/shared-contracts/` before implementation
- **No secrets in code** — AWS Secrets Manager / env vars only
- **No duplicate services** — check `services/` first
- **ADR for architecture forks** — use `docs/adr/SH-000-template.md`
- **Phase 1 first:** auth → shared-contracts → realtime → profiles before feature work

## Key Paths

| Resource | Path |
|----------|------|
| Multi-chat guide | `docs/MULTI-CHAT-EXECUTION-GUIDE.md` |
| Architecture | `docs/architecture-overview.md` |
| Agent validation | `node scripts/validate-agents.mjs` |
