## Tech Stack

Flutter (Riverpod, GoRouter) · NestJS · PostgreSQL · Redis · Socket.IO · Agora/Zego · AWS S3 · Cloudflare · Firebase Auth

Build **phase-by-phase**. Smallest correct diff. English in code; user strings via i18n ARB files.
